1
00:01:30,130 --> 00:01:33,780
<font face="Times New Roman" size="24"><b>1902</b></font>

2
00:01:34,210 --> 00:01:39,050
<font face="Times New Roman" size="12" color="#62000d"><b>{\an3}Episode Sixty
<font size="21">The Battle of Goryoukaku</font></b></font>

3
00:01:34,350 --> 00:01:37,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I can't imagine that the government, 
the de facto masters of Hokkaido,</font>

4
00:01:37,620 --> 00:01:43,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}are going to hand over the land just 
because we have this deed book.</font>

5
00:01:44,270 --> 00:01:46,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ask Enomoto Takeaki for help.</font>

6
00:01:46,820 --> 00:01:50,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And how are we supposed to 
meet somebody so important?</font>

7
00:01:50,620 --> 00:01:53,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Meiji government 
is after the deed book.</font>

8
00:01:53,930 --> 00:01:56,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's why we've hid it here.</font>

9
00:01:56,710 --> 00:02:01,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The deed book will be stolen 
before it gets to Enomoto-san.</font>

10
00:02:02,650 --> 00:02:05,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I know one Nispa who may help.</font>

11
00:02:07,310 --> 00:02:14,070
<font face="Times New Roman" size="24"><b>1869</b></font>

12
00:02:07,710 --> 00:02:11,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}When we were negotiating the 
land purchase with Enomoto-san,</font>

13
00:02:11,710 --> 00:02:14,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}we would often go to Goryoukaku.</font>

14
00:02:14,460 --> 00:02:18,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Without knowing that the Hakodate 
War was only going to get worse...</font>

15
00:02:18,860 --> 00:02:21,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kimuspu, water the horses, please.</font>

16
00:02:21,850 --> 00:02:22,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay.</font>

17
00:02:26,930 --> 00:02:28,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's an unusual tattoo.</font>

18
00:02:28,980 --> 00:02:30,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Does it mean anything?</font>

19
00:02:31,670 --> 00:02:32,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No...</font>

20
00:02:36,280 --> 00:02:37,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll help.</font>

21
00:02:37,400 --> 00:02:39,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I need to water my own horses, too.</font>

22
00:02:39,180 --> 00:02:41,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, it's all right, Nispa.</font>

23
00:02:42,070 --> 00:02:46,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are the Ainu who just went into 
the magistrate's office with you?</font>

24
00:02:46,060 --> 00:02:47,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

25
00:02:47,800 --> 00:02:51,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They'll buy the clams and 
seaweed we harvest, they say.</font>

26
00:02:51,840 --> 00:02:53,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

27
00:02:53,560 --> 00:02:56,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I leave Enomoto-san in 
charge of everything here.</font>

28
00:02:57,460 --> 00:03:01,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All I'm good with are 
battles, horses, and women.</font>

29
00:03:02,570 --> 00:03:06,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This handsome young man 
was, I later learned,</font>

30
00:03:06,600 --> 00:03:09,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">one of the leaders of the Ezo 
Republic, Hijikata Toshizou.</font>

31
00:03:10,470 --> 00:03:13,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Enomoto-san had not told Hijikata-san,</font>

32
00:03:13,120 --> 00:03:16,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">or any of his close allies, 
about the land purchase.</font>

33
00:03:17,180 --> 00:03:19,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The plan was carried out in secret.</font>

34
00:03:19,740 --> 00:03:24,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We were preparing to give the 
gold to the Ezo Republic.</font>

35
00:03:25,090 --> 00:03:26,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Keep your guard up.</font>

36
00:03:26,630 --> 00:03:30,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If they find out that we're hiding 
the gold in the Russian consulate,</font>

37
00:03:30,020 --> 00:03:31,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">they'll steal it all.</font>

38
00:03:31,750 --> 00:03:33,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If we can take out just what 
we're using for the deal,</font>

39
00:03:33,870 --> 00:03:36,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and split it up, 
carry it by land and by sea...</font>

40
00:03:37,050 --> 00:03:41,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But while we were preparing, the central 
government began an all-out attack.</font>

41
00:03:42,300 --> 00:03:44,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They fired their ships' 
guns from off the coast.</font>

42
00:03:44,910 --> 00:03:49,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The defeated soldiers set fire 
to the city. It was chaos.</font>

43
00:03:49,860 --> 00:03:52,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looks like everybody's 
fleeing to Mt. Hakodate.</font>

44
00:03:57,210 --> 00:03:59,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The handsome Nispa from before!</i></font>

45
00:04:03,070 --> 00:04:04,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Forget him!</font>

46
00:04:04,640 --> 00:04:07,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's with Enomoto-san!</font>

47
00:04:07,310 --> 00:04:08,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We have to help him!</font>

48
00:04:08,950 --> 00:04:11,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We treated him in an inn 
whose owner had fled,</font>

49
00:04:11,460 --> 00:04:15,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and helped him hide from 
the government's soldiers.</font>

50
00:04:15,850 --> 00:04:18,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The <i>Kaitenmaru</i> was burned.</font>

51
00:04:18,740 --> 00:04:21,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"The invincible Kaiten is nothing 
but bones," they're saying.</font>

52
00:04:24,410 --> 00:04:30,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The <i>Kaitenmaru</i> was a warship 
that Hijikata-san fought aboard.</font>

53
00:04:30,680 --> 00:04:33,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fort Benten Daiba is all that's left...</font>

54
00:04:33,930 --> 00:04:35,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We must protect it.</font>

55
00:04:36,120 --> 00:04:41,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Or the ships' guns will 
bring down Goryoukaku...</font>

56
00:04:43,170 --> 00:04:48,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He was shot on his way 
to reinforce Benten Daiba.</font>

57
00:04:48,350 --> 00:04:52,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The fort surrendered yesterday 
while you were asleep, Nispa.</font>

58
00:04:55,310 --> 00:04:56,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kimuspu-san...</font>

59
00:04:58,210 --> 00:04:59,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have a request...</font>

60
00:04:59,730 --> 00:05:02,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take me to Mt. Hakodate.</font>

61
00:05:19,790 --> 00:05:22,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've come to see this statue of Kannon?</font>

62
00:05:27,810 --> 00:05:33,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was the sound of ships' 
cannons firing on Goryoukaku.</font>

63
00:05:36,520 --> 00:05:38,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, you!</font>

64
00:05:39,610 --> 00:05:40,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I knew it!</font>

65
00:05:40,790 --> 00:05:42,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're Hijikata Toshizou!</font>

66
00:05:42,230 --> 00:05:43,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't shoot!</font>

67
00:05:43,690 --> 00:05:45,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought that if the Ezo Republic fell,</font>

68
00:05:45,820 --> 00:05:49,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the Ainu would lose their 
land. I was desperate.</font>

69
00:05:51,160 --> 00:05:52,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop it, Kimuspu!</font>

70
00:05:52,850 --> 00:05:54,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everyone will be killed!</font>

71
00:06:04,420 --> 00:06:05,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry...</font>

72
00:06:06,110 --> 00:06:09,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I won't forget the debt 
I owe you for saving me.</font>

73
00:06:10,120 --> 00:06:12,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I felt guilty for handing him 
over to the government's men,</font>

74
00:06:12,990 --> 00:06:16,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and never told Enomoto-san about him.</font>

75
00:06:17,900 --> 00:06:23,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But for some reason, I never heard 
any stories about Hijikata Toshizou</font>

76
00:06:23,170 --> 00:06:26,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">being arrested, or executed.</font>

77
00:06:27,310 --> 00:06:32,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Several years later, I heard rumors 
here and there that he was imprisoned.</font>

78
00:06:33,380 --> 00:06:36,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I once heard it from a man 
who was his jailer, too.</font>

79
00:06:36,760 --> 00:06:40,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hijikata Toshizou yet lives.</font>

80
00:06:41,630 --> 00:06:47,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Perhaps that Nispa may get word 
to Enomoto Takeaki for us.</font>

81
00:06:47,300 --> 00:06:50,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you going to become a prison 
guard and help him escape, then?</font>

82
00:06:51,730 --> 00:06:53,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hijikata Toshizou...</font>

83
00:06:54,190 --> 00:06:57,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After that, the Meiji government 
began to follow us.</font>

84
00:06:57,310 --> 00:07:00,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We killed many of theirs, 
and they killed many of ours.</font>

85
00:07:00,570 --> 00:07:03,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So we kept it hidden.</font>

86
00:07:03,670 --> 00:07:07,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The deed book, and this 
cursed gold, all of it.</font>

87
00:07:09,390 --> 00:07:11,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's move it somewhere else, for now.</font>

88
00:07:11,940 --> 00:07:15,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kimuspu, you told your younger brother 
about this consulate, right?</font>

89
00:07:16,180 --> 00:07:18,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know a good place.</font>

90
00:07:21,140 --> 00:07:23,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll hide the gold dust here,</font>

91
00:07:23,860 --> 00:07:26,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and try to inspire the Ainu to rise up.</font>

92
00:07:26,580 --> 00:07:30,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And if Hijikata Toshizou 
hasn't forgotten his debt...</font>

93
00:07:30,730 --> 00:07:33,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He'll help the Ainu in the future.</font>

94
00:07:34,830 --> 00:07:35,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Asirpa...</font>

95
00:07:46,040 --> 00:07:47,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}They're back!</font>

96
00:07:48,000 --> 00:07:49,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Into the holes!</font>

97
00:07:53,480 --> 00:07:54,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, shit!</font>

98
00:07:58,760 --> 00:07:59,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's started again.</font>

99
00:08:01,450 --> 00:08:02,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get out of there!</font>

100
00:08:02,610 --> 00:08:04,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All three of you, grab the rope!</font>

101
00:08:04,670 --> 00:08:07,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shiraishi, let's leave the gold for now.</font>

102
00:08:07,410 --> 00:08:09,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, I'm staying here!</font>

103
00:08:09,300 --> 00:08:12,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You idiot! One hit from that cannon 
and you'll be buried alive!</font>

104
00:08:34,430 --> 00:08:37,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're gonna have to stay 
holed up in here and fight.</font>

105
00:08:38,870 --> 00:08:41,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If we lose, we'll never
see the gold again!</font>

106
00:08:47,700 --> 00:08:50,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They didn't believe the 
deed book was real?</font>

107
00:08:50,210 --> 00:08:52,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We need to hurry!</font>

108
00:08:55,130 --> 00:08:57,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So they stopped firing the 
ships' cannons for a while</font>

109
00:08:57,950 --> 00:09:03,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">because Nagakura-san pretended to 
surrender and bought us time, I guess?</font>

110
00:09:07,560 --> 00:09:11,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nagakura told the truth 
about the deed book.</font>

111
00:09:12,150 --> 00:09:17,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's what I would do to get them to 
stop firing those cannons, if I were him.</font>

112
00:09:18,380 --> 00:09:23,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">During the Hakodate War, Goryoukaku 
had a tall magistrate's office in it.</font>

113
00:09:24,280 --> 00:09:28,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Meiji government targeted it with 
their warships from off the coast,</font>

114
00:09:29,020 --> 00:09:32,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">opening hole after hole in its roof.</font>

115
00:09:32,980 --> 00:09:35,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Ezo Republic couldn't 
take it, and surrendered.</font>

116
00:09:36,290 --> 00:09:38,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The government won the 
battle at Goryoukaku</font>

117
00:09:38,980 --> 00:09:41,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">without having to fight at close range.</font>

118
00:09:41,860 --> 00:09:46,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If there was any better way 
for the Ezo Republic to fight,</font>

119
00:09:47,260 --> 00:09:51,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it would've been to use fortifications 
to wait out the cannon fire.</font>

120
00:09:54,890 --> 00:09:59,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We don't have the magistrate's 
building to aim for.</font>

121
00:09:59,370 --> 00:10:05,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But we can use balloons to be far 
more accurate than we were then.</font>

122
00:10:08,610 --> 00:10:12,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're aiming solely for the 
fortifications we built on high ground.</font>

123
00:10:12,900 --> 00:10:15,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We learned during the Siege of Port Arthur</font>

124
00:10:15,810 --> 00:10:19,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">how dangerous those 
fortifications could be.</font>

125
00:10:19,930 --> 00:10:21,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, get inside!</font>

126
00:10:21,800 --> 00:10:23,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's dangerous out there!</font>

127
00:10:23,330 --> 00:10:28,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The key to strategy is limiting 
your opponent's options.</font>

128
00:10:32,470 --> 00:10:34,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The government of the Manchurian frontier</font>

129
00:10:34,930 --> 00:10:36,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">passed from military to civilian hands,</font>

130
00:10:36,940 --> 00:10:41,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and now it's falling apart as 
everyone scrambles for power.</font>

131
00:10:42,280 --> 00:10:47,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It won't be long before both Manchuria 
and Hokkaido are stolen by Russia!</font>

132
00:10:47,950 --> 00:10:50,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We must bring back military 
rule and concentrate</font>

133
00:10:50,250 --> 00:10:52,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">all power in Manchuria in its hands,</font>

134
00:10:52,090 --> 00:10:54,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">expanding our development of the frontier!</font>

135
00:10:54,770 --> 00:11:00,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We needed easily-sold gold 
for that to happen...</font>

136
00:11:02,140 --> 00:11:06,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But now what we need is 
the deed book it seems.</font>

137
00:11:06,260 --> 00:11:11,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But purchasing land in Hokkaido 
was always part of the plan!</font>

138
00:11:11,890 --> 00:11:14,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll defeat Hijikata 
Toshizou and his men,</font>

139
00:11:14,190 --> 00:11:16,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and recover the deed book!</font>

140
00:11:16,650 --> 00:11:18,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That book should be ours!</font>

141
00:11:19,240 --> 00:11:23,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll use the land to grow mass 
quantities of opium poppy!</font>

142
00:11:23,450 --> 00:11:26,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I expect that someday,</font>

143
00:11:26,040 --> 00:11:31,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the opium we harvest from it will 
be as valuable as gold in China!</font>

144
00:11:31,300 --> 00:11:35,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll use Hokkaido-grown opium 
to monopolize power in Manchuria,</font>

145
00:11:35,090 --> 00:11:38,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and start growing it there as well!</font>

146
00:11:38,630 --> 00:11:40,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The path to wealth for all 
of us can also be a way</font>

147
00:11:40,850 --> 00:11:44,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">of memorializing our fallen comrades!</font>

148
00:11:46,030 --> 00:11:52,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll cover the land where the ones I 
love sleep with opium poppy flowers!</font>

149
00:11:54,460 --> 00:11:56,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, here they come.</font>

150
00:12:00,530 --> 00:12:03,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Attack!</font>

151
00:12:04,030 --> 00:12:09,040
<font size="40"><b><font color="#0d0d0d">Golden Kamuy</font></b></font>

152
00:12:09,850 --> 00:12:14,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>After destroying the 
fortifications on high ground,</i></font>

153
00:12:14,940 --> 00:12:21,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>155 of Tsurumi's men all rushed the 
three bridges that lead into Goryoukaku!</i></font>

154
00:12:23,300 --> 00:12:26,300
<font face="Times New Roman" size="24"><b><font size="18">South Entrance</font></b></font>

155
00:12:28,310 --> 00:12:31,310
<font face="Times New Roman" size="24"><b><font size="18">North Entrance</font></b></font>

156
00:12:31,310 --> 00:12:34,270
<font face="Times New Roman" size="24"><b><font size="18">East Entrance</font></b></font>

157
00:12:34,500 --> 00:12:37,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hurry! Get inside Goryoukaku!</font>

158
00:12:37,120 --> 00:12:39,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get across the bridge 
as fast as you can!</font>

159
00:12:40,530 --> 00:12:42,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Knowledge of the deed book</i></font>

160
00:12:42,350 --> 00:12:47,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>took away the choice
of leveling Goryoukaku.</i></font>

161
00:12:47,670 --> 00:12:51,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The area a few dozen meters past 
the fortifications was unharmed.</i></font>

162
00:12:54,990 --> 00:12:57,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The fortifications we 
took out were decoys!</font>

163
00:13:00,680 --> 00:13:03,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The trees in the windbreak 
are 300 meters behind them,</font>

164
00:13:03,130 --> 00:13:05,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and too far for a retreat.</font>

165
00:13:05,880 --> 00:13:10,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's no place to hide on 
the outside of Goryoukaku.</font>

166
00:13:10,180 --> 00:13:12,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Keep going! Get inside!</font>

167
00:13:12,890 --> 00:13:14,640
<font face="Times New Roman" size="24"><b><font size="18">North Entrance</font></b></font>

168
00:13:17,770 --> 00:13:20,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Across the bridge! It's the only way!</font>

169
00:13:36,060 --> 00:13:38,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If there's no place to 
hide, jump in the moat!</font>

170
00:13:38,900 --> 00:13:40,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hide between the gaps in 
the bridge's supports!</font>

171
00:13:46,820 --> 00:13:49,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Order the ships to fire on 
the fortifications again!</font>

172
00:13:49,760 --> 00:13:52,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have them hit near the entrances, too!</font>

173
00:13:52,510 --> 00:13:53,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right!</font>

174
00:13:53,940 --> 00:13:55,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're too close to the fortifications!</font>

175
00:13:55,590 --> 00:13:58,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They'll hit Lieutenant Koito over there!</font>

176
00:13:58,620 --> 00:14:03,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's believe that he's 
worthy to be our flagbearer.</font>

177
00:14:15,390 --> 00:14:18,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have to protect the 
deed book no matter what!</font>

178
00:14:19,170 --> 00:14:23,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Survivors of the Boshin War, 
and survivors of the Russo-Japanese War...</font>

179
00:14:24,230 --> 00:14:26,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wonder which'll win.</font>

180
00:14:27,080 --> 00:14:29,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Experience or spirit.</font>

181
00:14:30,230 --> 00:14:32,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, that soldier.</font>

182
00:14:32,210 --> 00:14:33,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's sending a signal!</font>

183
00:14:33,960 --> 00:14:37,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's going to have them 
resume fire! Shoot!</font>

184
00:14:37,170 --> 00:14:38,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We can't have that!</font>

185
00:14:45,470 --> 00:14:46,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, I stopped them!</font>

186
00:14:49,900 --> 00:14:53,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Prepare all the grenades 
you have, Sergeant Tsukishima!</font>

187
00:14:53,030 --> 00:14:54,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gather up grenades!</font>

188
00:15:00,500 --> 00:15:02,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lieutenant Koito, follow me!</font>

189
00:15:08,410 --> 00:15:10,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take out the enemy on the high ground!</font>

190
00:15:21,540 --> 00:15:24,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Hang in there! Don't let them inside!</font>

191
00:15:25,590 --> 00:15:29,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hijikata-san, let's retreat 
to the trench behind us!</font>

192
00:15:29,150 --> 00:15:34,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, if we fall back they'll charge at 
us through their own cannon blasts!</font>

193
00:15:34,550 --> 00:15:35,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We must stop them here!</font>

194
00:15:35,830 --> 00:15:38,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll all be blown to shreds at this rate.</font>

195
00:15:38,620 --> 00:15:41,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll believe in Kadokura's luck.</font>

196
00:15:47,610 --> 00:15:49,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is the Kannon statue!</font>

197
00:15:50,620 --> 00:15:52,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kannon-sama will have to move.</font>

198
00:15:58,670 --> 00:15:59,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is this?</font>

199
00:16:00,330 --> 00:16:02,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">During the Battle of Hakodate,</font>

200
00:16:02,720 --> 00:16:06,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hijikata-san and the Shinsengumi
hid it here, I'm told.</font>

201
00:16:14,570 --> 00:16:16,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The <i>Kaitenmaru</i>'s main gun.</font>

202
00:16:26,520 --> 00:16:28,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If the deed book is real,</font>

203
00:16:28,360 --> 00:16:33,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">either Immortal Sugimoto, 
Hijikata Toshizou, or Asirpa has it!</font>

204
00:16:33,470 --> 00:16:36,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They should be somewhere inside
Goryoukaku, trying to dodge cannon fire.</font>

205
00:16:37,400 --> 00:16:40,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll capture Goryoukaku and take it!</font>

206
00:16:41,130 --> 00:16:45,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I send the soldiers in, the enemy's 
defense will collapse from the inside.</font>

207
00:16:46,050 --> 00:16:49,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We will be the spear that 
collapses their defenses!</font>

208
00:16:58,610 --> 00:17:00,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's cross the bridge between shots!</font>

209
00:17:00,910 --> 00:17:02,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're sitting ducks out here!</font>

210
00:17:02,840 --> 00:17:05,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, wait for Lieutenant Tsurumi's signal!</font>

211
00:17:05,790 --> 00:17:08,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look! It's Lieutenant Tsurumi!</font>

212
00:17:09,810 --> 00:17:10,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}The enemy!</font>

213
00:17:25,000 --> 00:17:26,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't get scared!</font>

214
00:17:26,110 --> 00:17:27,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If your daddy loves you,</font>

215
00:17:27,480 --> 00:17:29,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">then his shells won't land on you!</font>

216
00:17:40,070 --> 00:17:41,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just a little more...</font>

217
00:17:41,370 --> 00:17:46,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Once the cannons blow a few 
more of them away, we charge!</font>

218
00:17:47,100 --> 00:17:49,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}We're finished, Sofia! Let's fall back!</font>

219
00:17:50,230 --> 00:17:52,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Get in the holes! I'll stay here!</font>

220
00:17:55,340 --> 00:17:56,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Near miss off the starboard bow!</font>

221
00:17:56,750 --> 00:17:58,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">An attack from Goryoukaku?</font>

222
00:17:58,680 --> 00:18:00,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All ships, hurry and weigh anchor!</font>

223
00:18:06,310 --> 00:18:07,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hurry.</font>

224
00:18:07,580 --> 00:18:11,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Right... little to the right. Right.</font>

225
00:18:15,980 --> 00:18:20,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The four destroyers had lowered 
their anchors to make their shots</i></font>

226
00:18:20,410 --> 00:18:22,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>on the Goryoukaku more accurate,</i></font>

227
00:18:22,470 --> 00:18:24,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>which made them slow to react.</i></font>

228
00:18:29,960 --> 00:18:31,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Got 'em!</font>

229
00:18:31,220 --> 00:18:32,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes!</font>

230
00:18:33,140 --> 00:18:35,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mansur, you're amazing!</font>

231
00:18:35,250 --> 00:18:38,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You hit 'em with this antique gun!</font>

232
00:18:38,290 --> 00:18:42,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sophia said you were one 
hell of an artilleryman!</font>

233
00:18:43,390 --> 00:18:46,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hurry! Keep 'em coming!</font>

234
00:18:46,350 --> 00:18:50,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ship #2, <i>Inazuma</i>, has taken 
a hit! It's burning!</font>

235
00:18:50,140 --> 00:18:52,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gunfire coming from Mt. 
Hakodate to our starboard!</font>

236
00:18:52,590 --> 00:18:53,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cut anchors!</font>

237
00:18:53,640 --> 00:18:56,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fleet, begin advancing at minimum speed!</font>

238
00:18:57,390 --> 00:18:59,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gun loaded!</font>

239
00:19:02,620 --> 00:19:05,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ship #3, <i>Akebono</i>, has taken a hit!</font>

240
00:19:05,440 --> 00:19:07,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ship #2, <i>Inazuma</i>, is burning!</font>

241
00:19:09,370 --> 00:19:12,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ship #4, <i>Oboro</i>, has taken a hit!</font>

242
00:19:16,950 --> 00:19:18,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's going to explode!</font>

243
00:19:18,210 --> 00:19:19,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get away from it!</font>

244
00:19:24,780 --> 00:19:26,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, look! The balloon!</font>

245
00:19:26,930 --> 00:19:29,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The cannons stopped, too!</font>

246
00:19:29,080 --> 00:19:30,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did Kadokura's group pull it off?</font>

247
00:19:30,970 --> 00:19:34,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We protected Goryoukaku with 
the <i>Kaitenmaru</i>'s main gun.</font>

248
00:19:35,200 --> 00:19:37,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's one of the things I 
didn't get to do last time.</font>

249
00:19:42,740 --> 00:19:46,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fleet, turn eight points to starboard!</font>

250
00:19:46,120 --> 00:19:49,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ship #4, <i>Oboro</i>, moderately 
damaged and on fire!</font>

251
00:19:49,550 --> 00:19:52,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This ship, the <i>Ikazuchi</i>, 
is the only one still unharmed!</font>

252
00:19:54,130 --> 00:19:55,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fire all weapons!</font>

253
00:19:55,620 --> 00:19:58,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Our target is the enemy on Mt. 
Hakodate to our port side!</font>

254
00:20:00,820 --> 00:20:05,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All guns, fire when ready!</font>

255
00:20:09,330 --> 00:20:10,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They hit back!</font>

256
00:20:10,680 --> 00:20:12,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shit! Run!</font>

257
00:20:22,520 --> 00:20:24,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mansur, stand up!</font>

258
00:20:24,300 --> 00:20:25,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hit him back!</font>

259
00:20:27,240 --> 00:20:28,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kirawus, we've done enough!</font>

260
00:20:28,940 --> 00:20:29,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We need to run!</font>

261
00:20:29,830 --> 00:20:32,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We need to take down that ship!</font>

262
00:20:47,850 --> 00:20:49,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're hit!</font>

263
00:20:50,010 --> 00:20:51,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fire back!</font>

264
00:20:59,980 --> 00:21:01,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Abandon ship!</font>

265
00:21:01,790 --> 00:21:03,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Prepare the lifeboats!</font>

266
00:21:03,860 --> 00:21:07,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Commander Koito!
Please head to the lifeboats!</font>

267
00:21:07,300 --> 00:21:09,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll stay with the ship.</font>

268
00:21:09,250 --> 00:21:10,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Commander Koito!</font>

269
00:21:13,210 --> 00:21:15,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Forget me! Abandon ship!</font>

270
00:21:15,450 --> 00:21:17,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is an order!</font>

271
00:21:22,280 --> 00:21:23,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Otonoshin...</i></font>

272
00:21:37,880 --> 00:21:40,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's the signal!</font>

273
00:21:40,270 --> 00:21:42,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They've taken the high ground on one side!</font>

274
00:21:42,780 --> 00:21:44,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look under the bridge!</font>

275
00:21:44,450 --> 00:21:46,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They got down there somehow!</font>

276
00:21:46,540 --> 00:21:48,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't hear any gunfire from that hill.</font>

277
00:21:49,340 --> 00:21:51,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Were they all taken out?</font>

278
00:23:35,160 --> 00:23:40,250
<font face="Times New Roman" size="12" color="#62000d"><b>{\an3}<font size="17">Next time
<font size="27">Bushido</font></font></b></font>

279
00:23:35,890 --> 00:23:39,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Next time: Bushido!</i></font>

